Well this one's a bit weird.

1. At 2:49, the game has a small seizure.

2. At 33:56, the game outright crashed, seemingly due to running out memory when loading the level complete textures. I get started again at 36:42. Not sure I can blame the game for the crash, considering my PC's been acting up lately. Here's the crash log: https://pastebin.com/QdTzerNx

3. At the very end, Chrome crashes and the error message steals focus from the game, so I panic and stop the recording to make sure it doesn't get corrupted. The continued recording is at https://youtu.be/QGkeuYinyFA (basically just to keep a record of deaths and chapter times)
